{"tid":15431,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過明明仲好鍾意對方但都係忍唔住講分手？","createTime":"2016-12-01T03:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T04:08:18.000Z","uid":40899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d65b97336832b5d545d75016eb9649e82919d90","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係嘈嘈下交冇思考過就爆出黎果種，係真係有考慮過分手會對佢/大家更好既果種<br />\n歡迎大家留低自己既經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉：<br />\n初戀果次一開始係對方鍾意我先，但後尾發覺到佢已經冷淡左，本身晚晚傾電話，突然連續好幾晚冇打黎，msn sms 都少左好多，亦都冇再一齊放學，好似避緊我咁，最後忍唔住講左分手<br />\n<br />\n雖然講分手係自己，但打擊依然好大<br />\n最後用左兩年幾時間恢復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df29270920253b18e09499630c05597c7d0535a","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61a41b5ae34ad05fc94b3090f73c4a037aded58","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1890cf84d1349e83d8e3b7d46c0581bb7a20402","tid":15431,"uid":44300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:54:09.000Z","msg":"反而試過以為自己好鐘意對方，但因為一啲野而講左分手，分左之後竟然覺得冇咩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704bceece78f50257986d34720598fc757ef03c8","tid":15431,"uid":28941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"同你差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用左年幾時間恢復"},{"pid":"21d723ffc2e3b49e784bc795f9e5b83344adf3e9","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而試過以為自己好鐘意對方，但因為一啲野而講左分手，分左之後竟然覺得冇咩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好事黎既 雙方早啲解決"},{"pid":"893a9e0f5c1da546d638ad93da0b541e7f2faf70","tid":15431,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:57:12.000Z","msg":"過咗去望翻轉頭就會覺得自己好蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8270a2ebc5d4c4d29745f9acf9d7b59377cf5f79","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用左年幾時間恢復</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年sad到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇胃口食野 又狂寫叫春文<br />\n寫到之後果幾個月內完全作唔到文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593005709d2a199efe117cc3e63f509055b17616","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過咗去望翻轉頭就會覺得自己好蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人誰無on9過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57dffeb366a88cddf1ba153652ed3a28d1be911c","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>反而試過以為自己好鐘意對方，但因為一啲野而講左分手，分左之後竟然覺得冇咩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好事黎既 雙方早啲解<del>決</del><span style=\"color: red;\">脫</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ef17c4746969d34fd7140640597e973659626cb7","tid":15431,"uid":6786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">初戀果次一開始係對方鍾意我先，但後尾發覺到佢已經冷淡左，本身晚晚傾電話，突然連續好幾晚冇打黎，msn sms 都少左好多</span>，亦都冇再一齊放學，好似避緊我咁，最後忍唔住講左分手</blockquote><br />\n然後發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即時斬纜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a85f5ee2f00a12026226b56aa663ca0528ee94","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:00:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">初戀果次一開始係對方鍾意我先，但後尾發覺到佢已經冷淡左，本身晚晚傾電話，突然連續好幾晚冇打黎，msn sms 都少左好多</span>，亦都冇再一齊放學，好似避緊我咁，最後忍唔住講左分手</blockquote><br />\n然後發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即時斬纜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊果陣有人追佢 不過佢地冇一齊<br />\n以上係分手後好耐先知"},{"pid":"80390efed5d507a15ef716acbca7c9fd4aa38827","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:03:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">初戀果次一開始係對方鍾意我先，但後尾發覺到佢已經冷淡左，本身晚晚傾電話，突然連續好幾晚冇打黎，msn sms 都少左好多</span>，亦都冇再一齊放學，好似避緊我咁，最後忍唔住講左分手</blockquote><br />\n然後發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即時斬纜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊果陣有人追佢 不過佢地冇一齊<br />\n以上係分手後好耐先知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而且追佢既係網友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n得知後既我從此入左網戀坑好幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a60f883a21f895023b0dadff2a143f62ebce1f5","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:40:40.000Z","msg":"另一次係大約兩年前<br />\n因為唔想自己一味付出而對方完全冇點回應依個情況持續落去<br />\n知道自己總有一日會頂唔順依種感覺<br />\n寧願提早斬<br />\n<br />\n果日講完又係唱住歌喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e01390a9fbf483dbdc7b444f7b2c86068b0460d","tid":15431,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:45:44.000Z","msg":"同你差唔多一模一樣 <br />\n明明佢鍾意我先<br />\n但係一齊之後我就越愛越深 佢就開始淡 <br />\n最後覺得佢已經唔care我 幾鍾意佢都好 最後都係自己講左分手"},{"pid":"399286c869a9736b392b4e9684e021966013e290","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:50:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你差唔多一模一樣 <br />\n明明佢鍾意我先<br />\n但係一齊之後我就越愛越深 佢就開始淡 <br />\n最後覺得佢已經唔care我 幾鍾意佢都好 最後都係自己講左分手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd5f219a3dedfb571ba6c3cfcd98d63d304962f","tid":15431,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:03:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同你差唔多一模一樣 <br />\n明明佢鍾意我先<br />\n但係一齊之後我就越愛越深 佢就開始淡 <br />\n最後覺得佢已經唔care我 幾鍾意佢都好 最後都係自己講左分手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜過左3年我個心都仲有佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a56d29b02f571f94e087e79b769ef490de574e","tid":15431,"uid":45627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"初初係好鐘意, 不過對方成日都玩失蹤<br />\n我好信得過佢冇帽我, 但係慢慢感情都變淡<br />\n似朋友多過情侶, 同對方講左幾次話會改, 結果都係&hellip;<br />\n最後忍唔住講分手, 反而個人輕鬆好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976e9e559190ce58bda993da95b9fdb8ff15bced","tid":15431,"uid":17932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:53:33.000Z","msg":"9個月，9日recover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8fb4ede30493a6811b1f854f6ebfeb31141989","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:27:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同你差唔多一模一樣 <br />\n明明佢鍾意我先<br />\n但係一齊之後我就越愛越深 佢就開始淡 <br />\n最後覺得佢已經唔care我 幾鍾意佢都好 最後都係自己講左分手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜過左3年我個心都仲有佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好記得當年一齊廿幾日 到我真係唔再諗起佢用左廿幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢慢黎啦 係需要時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba75c8fdb472bc1ca333be91d89e618b87a55852","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>初初係好鐘意, 不過對方成日都玩失蹤<br />\n我好信得過佢冇帽我, 但係慢慢感情都變淡<br />\n似朋友多過情侶, 同對方講左幾次話會改, 結果都係&hellip;<br />\n最後忍唔住講分手, 反而個人輕鬆好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時真係 覺得再同佢落去只係會繼續傷害自己<br />\n但自己又唔捨得 兩方面既諗法會好掙扎<br />\n早日解脫係好事黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c381168a24a716316a87a0a942ee7088823dfe4","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>9個月，9日recover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能巴打有晒心理準備"},{"pid":"be800ad84bd1e0fa10fd130fbc819bdfedf68fd0","tid":15431,"uid":11442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:33:24.000Z","msg":"有無人斬極都斬唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1196138c6e1ae41d4fa322b2b974f08442a6f23d","tid":15431,"uid":40899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人斬極都斬唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名<br />\n因為我一下定決心就好難改變返 所以冇依個問題"},{"pid":"7b55aa5c10656a31ecad67916164fd02d1dd7cb7","tid":15431,"uid":44549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人斬極都斬唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次失望同唔開心都係自己氹返自己<br />\n同自己講可能係我包容唔夠姐 <br />\n可能下次佢會做得更好呢 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢慢唔敢期望啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}